data.description: Make this adorable cottage your comfortable home.  This home has so much character.  There is a spacious addition on the back of the home that can serve as a oversized master bedroom or a secondary family room. West facing making the back yard ideal for hot summer evenings. The lot is nice sized and feels extra wide.  Some cosmetic updating will turn this charming bungalow into a personalized adorable home.
